    bibo:volume "55" ;
    dc:creator "Shi, Boyang; Chen, Xiaoyong; Pan, Da; Sun, Hongying" ;
    dc:date "2021" ;
    dc:title "First record of the freshwater crab genus Esanthelphusa Naiyanetr, 1994 (Decapoda: Brachyura: Gecarcinucidae) from Myanmar, with the description of a new species from the Kayin State" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767606>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767610>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767612>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767604>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767614> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767606>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Esanthelphusa kayinensis sp. nov., holotype, male, 31.58 × 25.34 mm, NNU16C-PA1 (a–e, g); paratypes, female, 29.65 × 24.49 mm, NNU16C-PA2 (f, h). (a) overall dorsal view; (b) overall ventral view; (c) frontal view of cephalothorax; (d) external view of major (left) chela; (e,f) ventral view of thoracic sternum with pleon; (g) thoracic sternum showing sterno-pleonal cavity and G1 in situ; h, thoracic sternum showing vulvae. White scale bar = 1.0 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5767606/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767610>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Esanthelphusa kayinensis sp. nov., holotype, male, NNU16C-PA1. (a) left third maxilliped; (b) ventral view of left G1; (c) dorsal view of left G1; (d) left G2; (e): ventral view of distal half of G1; f, dorsal view of distal half of G1. White scale bar = 1.0 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5767610/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767612>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Esanthelphusa kayinensis sp. nov.: (a, b) colour in life; (c) habitat." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5767612/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767604>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Map of Myanmar showing sampling sites (black circle) of Esanthelphusa kayinensis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5767604/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5767614>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Bayesian inference (BI) tree for the Esanthelphusa species and other freshwater crabs based on 16S rDNA sequences. Values at the nodes represent posterior probabilities and bootstrap values (BPP/BS). Five clades are recognised: Oceania clade (blue), Southeast Asia islands clade (yellow), China and Indochina Peninsula clade (orange), and Indian Peninsula clade (green). The new species is marked in bold and new sequences from the present study are indicated with asterisks." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5767614/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

